*******************************************************************************

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                              General Information
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Type.................: Application
Platform.............: Windows 9x/ME/2000/XP
More Info............: http://www.ezbsystems.com/easyboot/index.html


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                 Release Notes
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
EasyBoot is an integrated tool to create MultiBoot, Menu driven CDs & DVDs with native language. It has the ability to automatically 

produce boot image files, and generate the ISO file as well. Using your CD/DVD Recording software such as Nero or Roxio to Record the 

ISO, you get a bootable CD/DVD that completely belongs to you. You can customize it with your company&#039;s name or slogan or even use it 

for your clients.
Features:

Realize local language, multiple selections, and colorful menus on your bootable CD & DVD.
Create screen layouts, Insert text, menu bars and function keys with a full GUI
Preview the actual effects during the design process
Automatically generate boot loader and menu files
Directly build bootable ISO files that are ready to burn
	 
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                 Install Notes
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Install the app, open serial.txt and register app.
